{"tid":2511321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港男配烏克蘭Model｜24歲戰鬥民族嫁42歲香港MMA拳王「佢好似野獸咁性感」","createTime":"2021-04-30T22:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T01:04:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a3ac2b17e1dcf81567c1908fbee52f2153c3fc","tid":2511321,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T22:16:27.000Z","msg":"「Sana你掉了東西了。」「跌了甚麼？」「戒指。」剛剛才打完一場訓練賽，現在是全職MMA教練的朱國璋（Tony）單膝跪下，向剛剛鼻子被打中、頭髮亂了的烏克蘭女友Sana（Oksana Klim）求婚，Sana爆喊答應，這是一個港男與烏克蘭女的愛情故事。港男Tony今年40歲，小時候愛打機，日打8至10個鐘，高峯期胖至200磅，長大後成為電子工程師。有天，他突然想減肥，從小愛武術的他就去學拳，一學就愛上這種挑戰極限、拳拳到肉的運動，「因為唔懶得，一懶，就會俾人打。」2010年取得金腰帶，成為香港泰拳拳王，綽號「雷鳥」，現在他是全職私人MMA教練。Sana來自烏克蘭，21歲的她是一位模特兒，六年前來港工作，愛上這個五光十色，又被大自然圍繞的香港。「烏克蘭好少模特兒工作，即使有，人工都好少。香港係國際城市，好多國際品牌都鍾意搵歐洲面孔拍攝，比較多發展。」夢想是做專業化妝師，現在她除了工作外，會去做兼職司儀和上化妝課，想盡辦法留港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210501/7NZ7UJDG5FGDRCL6ALYIRCXIUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210501%2F7NZ7UJDG5FGDRCL6ALYIRCXIUU%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=82b84758\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210501%2F7NZ7UJDG5FGDRCL6ALYIRCXIUU%2F&h=8aaf1b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210501/7NZ7UJDG5FGDRCL6ALYIRCXIUU/</a>"},{"pid":"5cd4f2cacdd6657e242559469122d975f4abd9a2","tid":2511321,"uid":366655,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T22:20:34.000Z","msg":"肯定晚晚扑嘢扑唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d173f70dd2d4c875addac00d4e116a97ab111ff3","tid":2511321,"uid":190320,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"睇圖真係好羡慕個中坑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif